{"tid":1214471,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蔡英文勝出選總統！　35.67%強壓賴清德27.48%","createTime":"2019-06-13T04:29:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T17:25:09.000Z","uid":152104,"like":231,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"412090c698155aa8860b2ab97741efba291a7f37","tid":1214471,"uid":152104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:29:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/politics/realtime/20190613/1582361/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2Frealtime%2F20190613%2F1582361%2F&d=lXSk0n6jiDV9AqJ6X6RhLu2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=8eb4b59f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2Frealtime%2F20190613%2F1582361%2F&h=7ae3db33\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/politics/realtime/20190613/1582361/</a><br />\n<br />\n民進黨總統初選民調，今天結果揭曉，總統蔡英文擊敗對手、行政院前院長賴清德，蔡民調成績35.67%，賴清德27.48%，蔡領先8.2個百分點，獲得競選總統連任的門票。民進黨初選這一役，為台灣的民主歷史寫下新頁，中華民國憲政史上首位競選連任的總統，正面遭逢黨內對手挑戰，經歷將近3個月波折，最後終於透過台灣首次總統初選「手機合併市話」民調，讓人民做出選擇。黨內人士坦言「鬆一口氣」，但也表示，對未來整合有信心。<br />\n<br />\n612義士又幫到蔡總統贏初選<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65e3960a99fb95c4c70d435d28968e3699b7194f","tid":1214471,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:30:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"991d768c24e05f957e3ddb64f1aee145d582ee92","tid":1214471,"uid":89182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:30:09.000Z","msg":"雙贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1ed6f2bb4dfe7f7f9b36a266bcf20b164385313","tid":1214471,"uid":194501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:30:59.000Z","msg":"發大財<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aa52d508cc28c6a3024497bcfe2ee6bf47a0c28","ti